invariant itertools_extra178.pairwise_mro_len_2:
  description: "itertools.pairwise.__mro__.__len__() == 2 — pairwise is a C extension type inheriting directly from object; MRO is (pairwise, object); new to extra178"
  kind: python_call_eq
